</code></pre> Do-While Loop (Post-Test Loop) in Java<pre><code>// The Do-While Loop (Post-Test Loop) in Java
// this loop continues while the condition is true
public class DoWhileLoop {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int x = 0;

        do {                        // starts a do-while loop (a post-test loop)
            // your code goes here    // code inside the loop goes here
            System.out.println(x);
            x++;
        } while (x &lt;= 10);          // ends the do-while loop.
    }
}
</code></pre>

